This map is about a factory and the Near zone with some house and restaurant, there's a subway with different sites to barricade.

***MAP FEATURES***

- Medium sites of Barricade (rooms in factory,a house, subway rooms, and more..)
- Rain, few zm maps have it
- Awesome to play when there's few people in the server
- Last Version.
- Supported ( report bugs in feedback and ill fix it :) )
- Map in continue extension, so if you want a remake of this map tell me.
